content: No files or folders match this filter. Try another or remove the filter to view all files.

comment.text: "No files or folders match this filter. Try another or remove the filter to view all files." This translation key is used in a UI element to display a message when a file filter does not return any results, prompting the user to adjust their search or remove the filter. It appears in an empty filter container component.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The term 'hakuehtoja' (search conditions) is a bit too formal and technical for the intended meaning of 'filter'. A more natural phrasing would be 'suodatinta' or 'suodattimia'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Mikään tiedosto tai kansio ei vastaa suodatinta. Kokeile toista tai poista suodatin nähdäksesi kaikki tiedostot.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'զտիչը' (ztičը) is slightly awkward and less common in modern Armenian. While technically correct, 'ֆիլտրը' (filtrը) would be a more natural and widely understood equivalent for 'filter'.
The phrase "別のフィルタを適用するか" could be improved. While technically correct, it's a bit formal and clunky for a user interface. A more natural phrasing would be more user-friendly.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 別のフィルタを試すか、フィルタを解除してすべてのファイルを表示してください。

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The sentence structure is a bit long and could be broken into two shorter sentences for better readability in a UI.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: このフィルタに一致するファイルやフォルダはありません。別のフィルタを試すか、フィルタを解除してすべてのファイルを表示してください。

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ' is potentially a misspelling. It seems like a combination of 'ຕົວ' and 'ກັ່ນຕອງ', but the correct word is likely 'ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ' with the combining character.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ຕົວກັ່ນຕອງ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'ຂໍຈົ່ງລອງໃຊ້ອື່ນ' is a bit formal and could be simplified for a more natural flow. It's technically correct but sounds somewhat stiff.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ລອງໃຊ້ອື່ນ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "Filtru de fișier sau folder nu a produs rezultate" is a bit awkward. A more natural Romanian phrasing would be 'Niciun fișier sau folder nu corespunde acestui filtru'. The current phrasing feels overly literal and slightly unnatural.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Niciun fișier sau folder nu corespunde acestui filtru.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While not strictly incorrect, using "Încercați" instead of the more common "Încearcă" (informal) or "Încercați" (formal) for 'Try' might feel a little too formal in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Încearcă un alt filtru sau elimină filtrul pentru a afișa toate fișierele.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "සියලු ගොනු බැලීමට" (siyallu gonu balemita) literally translates to "to view all files". While understandable, it's slightly awkward in Sinhala. A more natural phrasing would be "සියලු ගොනු දැකීමට" (siyallu gonu dekimaata) or "සියලු ගොනු පරීක්ෂා කිරීමට" (siyallu gonu parikshaakemaata).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: සියලු ගොනු දැකීමට (siyallu gonu dekimaata) or සියලු ගොනු පරීක්ෂා කිරීමට (siyallu gonu parikshaakemaata)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The sentence structure could be improved for better flow.  Combining the two sentences into one, while maintaining clarity, would enhance readability.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: මෙම පෙරහනට ගැලපෙන ගොනු හෝ ෆෝල්ඩර නොමැත. සියලු ගොනු දැකීමට වෙනත් පෙරහනක් උත්සාහ කරන්න, නැත්නම් පෙරහන ඉවත් කරන්න.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'фасцикла' is often misspelled. The correct spelling is 'фасцикле'.
The phrase 'Pokušajte sa drugim' is a bit awkward. A more natural translation for 'Try another' would be 'Pokušajte sa drugim filterom' or simply 'Pokušajte drugi filter'.
